name: Set of 5 Envelopes and Cards - Pot Luck
description:
A pot luck selection - trust me! 
Hand silkscreen printed and hand made envelope and card boxed set.
A set of five hand screenprinted envelopes with matching cards.


Envelopes are printed all over and are secured with a sticker. 
Folded cards are C6 in size, each one is hand cut and folded.
If blended colours are your pick, it will change from item to item.
Due to the nature of hand screenprinting, every card and envelope will be slightly different and may have minor discrepancies - all the things that are part of the process of hand made.
